Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限的時間將跳動停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們悄聲無息地燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界已經脫軌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被紅世之火所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------OP-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そして　この空　赤く染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:31.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}また来る時　この一身で　進むだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:48.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違っていく‘人’も　紛れ失くした‘モノ’も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:53.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつかは　消えゆく記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:59.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}熱く揺るがす‘強さ’　儚く揺れる‘弱さ’
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:04.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所詮　同じ結末
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:10.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな日常　紅霞を溶かし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}現れる陽　紅る世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:21.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}風になびかせ　線を引いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:27.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}流れるような髪先　敵を刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:33.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振り斬った想い　漲る夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:38.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すべては今　この手で　使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:42.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}果たしてゆくだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}於是這片天空被染成紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:31.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再度來臨之際  唯以此身不斷向前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:48.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}擦肩而過之「人」  紛亂迷失之「物」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:53.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}終將成為  消失的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:59.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}熱烈震撼的「堅強」  虛無飄渺的「脆弱」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:04.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}終究是  同一結局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:10.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如此平凡  溶化於晚霞之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}升起的太陽  通紅的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:21.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}隨風飄揚  勾畫路線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:27.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}宛如飄揚的髮梢  刺向敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:33.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}揮刀斬斷的思念  瀰漫夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:42.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}一切都於此刻  僅以這雙手達成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夜明け生まれ来るものよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:04.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}決して見失わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:09.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You are you　少女よ　今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振りほどき立ちあがれ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:36.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸の傷を隠したまま　風を切り進む君を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:41.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ見守る術など何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:50.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}その瞳はずっと先の　自分を探しているの?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:58.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}でも聞こえるよ　深い悲しみの鼓動が叫んでる!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:03.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm just　夜明け前の暗闇が
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:06.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一生を運命づける
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大丈夫　少女よ　今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:15.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔やみ恥じることはない　Far way…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:22.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}十字を背負い　死ぬ気で炎を駆けろ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}拂曉降生的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:04.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}決不可迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:09.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You are you  少女啊  就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}掙開手站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:36.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}隱藏著胸口的傷痕  破風前進的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:41.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}除了注視  我別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:50.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你那瞳孔是否正在  探尋著前方的自我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:58.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不過我能夠聽見  你那深情悲戚的心正在吶喊著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:03.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm just  拂曉前的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:06.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}將此一生付為命運
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒事的  少女啊  就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:15.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒什麼好懊悔羞愧的  Far way…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:22.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}背負著十字架  以死的覺悟向著火焰疾走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:22.57,Optitle,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(315,240)}美麗的酒杯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  到底在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在封絕中一點點也不動的就是那混蛋傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於被發覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  撿骨師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的毀滅終於來到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  接受這熾熱的吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一生可只有一次的激烈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  想幹了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  想幹就幹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果又不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來完全不知道獵物在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道覺得這種程度的小把戲會管用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認命吧  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新自我介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是「天壤劫火」——亞拉斯托爾的火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎發灼眼的討伐者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是天壤劫火的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被擺了一道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是為了隱藏小鬼的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得不錯嘛  撿骨師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離遠些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  用了個頗為奇怪的手下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是密斯提斯嗎  而且竟然還在封絕中能動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  在你體內的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,複雜的事以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是發誓不對撿骨師拉米動手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是嘗點苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拽什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道以為能阻止我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要嘗點苦頭的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說準備包庇紅世之徒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是火霧戰士的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討伐他的話可能使城市陷入危機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅世之徒的存在更加危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉米是無害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  你說無害的紅世之徒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西  你真以為存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想和你爭論
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒精神來教育你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是罷手還是吃苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好  我們的回答是第3個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些傢伙一個都別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果辦的到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你變的很有殺掉的價值了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  上吧上吧  幹掉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很精彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我們這裡移除了那傢伙的敵意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只集中到她自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎麗  在太陽公公的周圍轉啊轉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在後面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有悠二在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量就湧出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事都做的到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東躥西躥的  可惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包庇拉米那混帳傢伙是使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火霧戰士的使命可是討伐紅世之徒喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是守護這個世界與紅世的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為了這個使命而去討伐有害的紅世之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你只是想殺才去殺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有什麼不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都不懂的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我可不知道你的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是覺得你礙事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  瑪裘莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的啦  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這小鬼確實改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻不是戰鬥樣式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是更加內在的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠帶來這令人厭煩的自信的什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨降綠坪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勿沾吾身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是避火戒指嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為會沒有任何對策就把悠二晾在一邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們  是等著我來襲擊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  自在式崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討伐紅世之徒還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐很令人擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣  又能做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:10:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二  把身體貼緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來火焰就不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在解開的話就全中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  是掉下去還是被打中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次輪到你選了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這又是少見的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是難得的好戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別想逃  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在  解開結界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何事  都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別慌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就能控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二  抓緊身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能好好飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事都做的到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  這次真的結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:12:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漫長啊  這追逐遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始  就沒什麼重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被奪去一切的活著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我想毀掉一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才去破壞  殺戮    搶奪  嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  只是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是這個都被那傢伙奪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了向我炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經  連破壞的東西都沒剩下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空無一物了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少有他就行了  至少有他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說說看吧  以後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是空無一物的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鑲有群青色的漂亮容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼喚我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用充滿殺意的怒吼呼喚我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來填滿你的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來滿足我的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  呼喚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我美麗的酒杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹂躪的爪牙--馬爾克希亞斯的顯現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去封絕會解開的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一解開的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和外部連接起來的話就不可能修復了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面的人都會死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他憎惡的悲鳴正無序地流出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕封絕外也受到影響了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是事到如今道理已經說不通了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就打到他聽話為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我可以幫忙的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為要用盡全力跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當我喊的時候就用戒指張開最小限度的結界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  要抓住你了  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就看不見前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  那個  這裡莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁我攻擊瞬間的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用「湛藍」來防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會發暗號的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和剛才一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何事都做的到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次感覺到了夏娜的殺意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧你還沒殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換了你們的話可能會殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是火霧戰士的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  火霧戰士的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你嚐到苦頭後大概再也不會追拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所能做的事到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是說使命使命的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像紅世之王一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說些孩子氣的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  現在還沒想幹些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為剛被蹂躪的爪牙威脅過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果對我的酒杯出手的話就把你們全咬死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也沒變過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰管什麼世界的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把周圍的存在都吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你們殺啊殺啊殺個精光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別追銀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋  你知道銀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個光追是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追不到  找不出  平白無故地出現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能因為這話就徹底放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個到了該來的時期必然會遇見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候該如何接受和行動就是你的自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個銀到底是什麼東西    不能說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不問了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來  給破壞的那麼徹底
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒有餘力來修復了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是零時迷子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算用光你的存在也不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天壤劫火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有炎發灼眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也讓你幫了不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你把城市修復了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枉費你特地收集的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當成是達成願望時的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣想的話就覺得便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概多少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我想問今天用掉的力量大概要收集多久才有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個來你的事更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是不準備光等著消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是零時迷子的話情況又不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嗎  雖然是不用擔心會消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是消失不消失的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  零時迷子和火霧戰士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將來誰也不知道  有緣再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心  這樣說可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再會了  天壤劫火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在因果的十字路口再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望何時你的願望之花能盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋風琴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋的……！？那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋風琴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是紅世之徒裡最高級的自在師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,編出了許多的自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撿骨師或是拉米這些通稱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是達成自己目的之前在這個世界徘徊虛假頭銜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花費數百年所為了達成的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是他心裡所留下的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喀嗒喀嗒  瑪裘莉·頓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賣了床  睡大覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼詞朗誦者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們既不打算懲戒也不打算教訓你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的行動偏離火霧戰士的使命時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會再次阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要明白這就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別殺那個別追這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要破壞不要搶奪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還剩什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  馬爾克希亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是狼狽到可笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是空無一物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是品行惡劣的女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可千萬別說「有我在」這種老土的台詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦  看下面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來安身之所還留著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是初學者啦  鍛煉的時候稍微留情點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己提出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學和小緣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天兩人也沒來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的  肯定不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃光的水
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.33,0:24:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耀眼的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.88,0:24:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在室內游泳池所蔓延的女人之間的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.64,0:24:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡只有泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.01,0:24:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛和欲望的游泳池畔
